               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 4r-134v)&#xD;
- Säqoqawä näfs “Lament of the Soul” (fols. 12vb l.20-16vb l.11)&#xD;
- Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 116rb l.2–120vb, l.22)&#xD;
- Homily of ʾAbbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 125rb l.6–127ra l.10)&#xD;
- Ṣalota burāke za-ʾanǝst “The Prayer of the Blessing for Women” (fol. 134ra l.1–vb l.8)&#xD;
&#xD;
Colophon.</summary>
